document.full_text: billy white had 16 points and 13 rebounds and kawhi leonard sealed san diego state's exhausting, 71-64 double-overtime victory over temple with a steal and a slam dunk.
document.title: west: san diego state 71, temple 64: white and leonard lead aztecs past temple in double overtime
